OL,3,CRicky Tomlinson & Sue Johnston reunite
OL,4,Cfor new travel show
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, he joined Lucy Meacock and
OL,7,FRob Smith in the ITV Granada studio to
OL,8,Freveal all about the new show. He
OL,9,Fsaid: "The highlight was working with
OL,10,FSue again, and discussing our
OL,11,Fdifferent paths!"
OL,13,F"Both Sue and I are from really
OL,14,Fworking class families, and obviously
OL,15,Fthere were no holidays abroad in those
OL,16,Fdays. It was New Brighton, like it or
OL,17,Flump it!
OL,19,FThe Royle Family actor is working as
OL,20,Fhard as ever, despite being 84 years
OL,21,Fof age.
