OL,3,CRicky Tomlinson & Sue Johnston reunite
OL,4,Cfor new travel show
OL,6,FThey'll travel to Shrewsbury Prison,
OL,7,Fwhere Ricky was jailed in the 1970s
OL,8,Ffor unjust charges that Sue,
OL,9,Fcoincidentally, took to the streets to
OL,10,Fcampaign against, and reveals how they
OL,11,Fboth ended up on Brookside Close,
OL,12,Fwhere the pair first acted alongside
OL,13,Feach other in the iconic Channel 4
OL,14,Fsoap opera.
