OL,3,CRicky Tomlinson & Sue Johnston reunite
OL,4,Cfor new travel show
OL,6,FAs well as playing Bobby and Sheila
OL,7,FGrant in Brookside, Ricky Tomlinson
OL,8,Fand Sue Johnston went on to become the
OL,9,Fequally iconic Jim and Barbara Royle
OL,10,Fin The Royle Family and have recently
OL,11,Fbeen sharing a sofa on Celebrity
OL,12,FGogglebox.
OL,14,FTelling ITV Granada about how their
OL,15,Fworking relationship began on , Ricky
OL,16,Fsaid: "We just got on together. We did
OL,17,Fhave one thing in common, we're both
OL,18,FLiverpool supporters. Although I don't
OL,19,Freally want to talk about that at the
OL,20,Fmoment..!"
