OL,3,CRicky Tomlinson & Sue Johnston reunite
OL,4,Cfor new travel show
OL,6,FTalking about the new show, Ricky
OL,7,Fsaid: "Sue and I have had a lot of
OL,8,Flaughs and a lot of memories over the
OL,9,Fyears. This new series will give us a
OL,10,Fchance to put the world to rights as
OL,11,Fwe explore places treasured to us and
OL,12,Fto many others around Britain."
