OL,3,CRicky Tomlinson & Sue Johnston reunite
OL,4,Cfor new travel show
OL,6,FMeanwhile Sue said: "Ricky and I feel
OL,7,Fso honoured to have had shared 40
OL,8,Fyears on screen together and a firm
OL,9,Ffriendship for all of that time, so
OL,10,Fit's particularly special to be taking
OL,11,Fa trip of a lifetime with him around
OL,12,Fthis beautiful country for More 4.
OL,13,FChannel 4 will have a job to do
OL,14,Fkeeping us both on our best behaviour
OL,15,Falong with the friends we meet along
OL,16,Fthe way."
OL,18,FBoth actors have remained in the North
OL,19,FWest all of their lives.
