OL,3,CRicky Tomlinson & Sue Johnston reunite
OL,4,Cfor new travel show
OL,6,F"I don't want to live anywhere else,
OL,7,FSue doesn't want to live anywhere
OL,8,Felse. I love where I am, I love the
OL,9,Flocal people where I am. I've had
OL,10,Fgreat neighbours."
OL,12,FThe series will see the pair out of
OL,13,Ftheir natural habitat in the North
OL,14,FWest, as they hit the road together.
OL,15,FThe three-part series Ricky, Sue & a
OL,16,FTrip or Two, will air for the first
OL,17,Ftime on Tuesday night at 9pm on More4.
